▋ Verify & Extract Manually
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  Open a terminal and change to the directory containing these files, then:

  1. Verify the payload has not been tampered with:

       minisign -V -p minisign.pub -m ${PAYLOAD_NAME}

     You should see: Signature and comment signature verified

  2. Extract the contents:

       tar xJf ${PAYLOAD_NAME}

  The files are now in your current directory.


